    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Paper size, generally used in Great Britain, measuring 15 by 20 inches (in the United States, 15 by 19 inches). Crown paper was originally watermarked with the insignia of a crown.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000114707/Oxford English Dictionary Online (2002-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Dimensión de papel, generalmente usado en Gran Bretaña que mide 15 por 20 pulgadas (en los Estados Unidos es de 15 por 19 pulgadas). El papel crown presentaba originalmente una marca de agua con la insignia de una corona.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Papierformaat in Groot-Brittannië algemeen wordt gebruikt, ter grootte van 381 x 508 mm (in de Verenigde Staten 381 x 483 mm). Crownpapier had oorspronkelijk een kroon als watermerk.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>紙張尺寸，多見於英國，約15 x 20 英吋（在美國為15 x 19 英吋）。最初的皇冠紙上有皇冠徽章的浮水印圖案。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
